      "title": "Found Footage",
      "desc": "Ranked found footage horror list based on my analysis and opinion. Footage must originate from a diegetic source.\n\nBecause I'll defend the form forever. 📹👻👹👽🧟🔪\n\nYes, I’ve really watched all of these. \n\nContact me if you’d like me to write/talk about found footage somewhere!\n\nIf you have a found footage film that isn’t on this list — short or feature — let me know so I can watch, review, rate, and rank it.\n\n\n1st film — The Blair Witch Project (1999) — watched in 1999 \n500th film — オカルト (2009) — watched 4/2/2025",
